 directive guidance and to exist beyond human conception.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 07. Mrz 2024) 0aGodxLove. 0aGodxWorship and love. 0aLovexReligious aspects. 0aLove. 4aPhilosophy : Philosophy of Religion. 4aPhilosophy : Philosophy. 4aReligion and Spirituality : Religion. 4aReligion and Spirituality : Theology. 7aPHILOSOPHY / Religious.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertSUNY Press eBook Package 2018z978311149142440uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781438471792423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781438471792/original  a978-3-11-149142-4  SUNY Press eBook Package 2018b2018  aGBV-deGruyter-alles